## Base tools every mode's scripts depend on. Plain main/universe Ubuntu
## packages only — nothing here needs an extra apt repo, multiverse, or
## i386 multiarch added at build time (see iso/README.md for why those are
## deliberately deferred to post-boot setup scripts instead of guessed at
## here).
curl
jq
git
build-essential
cmake
linux-tools-common
linux-tools-generic
power-profiles-daemon
flatpak
gnome-shell-extensions
gnome-tweaks
mokutil
ffmpeg
openssh-server
